    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m looking for a new home for my absolute gem of a car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still running like a total champ! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's ready to hit the road for many more adventures with you. Whether you're commuting or heading out for a weekend getaway, this beauty won't let you down. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
