    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously cared-for 2017 Porsche Macan S finished in Volcano Grey Metallic. This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and practicality. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, showing only minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small hairline scratch on the rear passenger door\u2014typical for a well-loved daily driver. Inside, the Agate Grey leather interior is in excellent shape; the seats are firm and the leather is supple, with only light creasing on the driver's side bolster. All electronics, including the Bose Surround Sound system and navigation, function perfectly. Mechanically, this Macan is top-tier. It has a full service history with a recent major interval completed, including new spark plugs and a PDK transmission fluid flush. The Michelin Latitude Sport 3 tires have roughly 70% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. No oil leaks, no warning lights, and a clean title in hand. This is a turn-key performance SUV ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 34800.0,
